## Project Conventions

### Directory Structure
- `Assets/Scripts/` - Game Code
- `Assets/Prefabs/` - Prefabs
- `Assets/Scenes/` - Scene Files
- `Assets/ScriptableObjects/` - Configuration Assets
- `openspec/` - OpenSpec Specification Files

### Code Standards
- Namespace: `{{PROJECT_NAMESPACE}}.{ModuleName}`
- Singleton Pattern: Use `Instance` property, provide `ResetInstance()` test method
- Event System: Publish/Subscribe via `EventBus` static class

### Test Standards
- EditMode Tests: `Assets/_Project/Tests/EditMode/`
- PlayMode Tests: `Assets/_Project/Tests/PlayMode/`
- Must run `test-unity` verification after completing each feature module
